# AI Pal Feature

## Overview
The AI Pal is an intelligent chat assistant that helps users with pet care questions and provides a pet matching quiz to recommend suitable pets based on lifestyle.

## Screen Structure

### AIScreen (Main)
- **Location**: `lib/features/ai/ai_screen.dart`
- **Components**:
  - Header with "AI Pal" title (centered)
  - Featured quiz card (prominent, softCoral accent)
  - Quick reply chips (preset topics)
  - Chat message list (scrollable)
  - Input bar (sticky at bottom, above nav bar)

### PetTestScreen (Quiz)
- **Location**: `lib/features/ai/pet_test_screen.dart`
- **Components**:
  - Close button (X icon, top-left)
  - Progress bar (shows current question / total)
  - Question text (large, bold)
  - Multiple choice options (radio buttons)
  - Next/Submit button (softCoral)
  - Result screen (shows after completion)

